name: TurboTax 2018 Tax Return
summary: A TAX2018 file is a United States tax return created with the 2018 version of Intuit TurboTax. It contains tax data, which includes personal information, federal IRS tax forms, and one or more state forms for the 2018 tax year. TAX2018 files may be encrypted if saved with password protection since they store sensitive personal and financial data.
